December Books are Now Open 

PLEASE READ BELOW 
________________

After careful consideration, thoughtful reflection, and a few heartfelt moments, I find myself compelled to share this announcement. 

I’ve sat, contemplated, postponed and even shed a few tears while making this post. As I open my books for December, I’m also closing a small chapter on my life. 

As I embark on a new chapter in my journey, I must inform you that December will mark the conclusion of my full-time availability for clients in Savannah, Ga. This decision stems from my desire to expand my horizons and pursue further growth as a beauty connoisseur.

I cant express my appreciation for your years of loyalty and support; you’ve all helped me grow so much both creatively and personally. 

See you soon 

PLEASE BOOK ACCORDINGLY AS AVAILABILITY IS LIMITED! 🤍
